---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import player from "../../../public/assets/success-player.svg";
---  
<div class="w-full overflow-hidden flex justify-center items-center bg-gradient-to-b from-[black] to-[#00000031]  relative top-[-2px]"> 
    <div class="w-[90%]  flex flex-col justify-center items-center pb-12 ">
        <div class="w-full flex items-center justify-start ">
            <p class="font-bold text-[48px] leading-[60px] uppercase tracking-[0%] bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-[#9E9B9B] bg-clip-text text-transparent pt-16 max-lg:text-[32px] max-lg:leading-10">Success Stories:<br/> From Overlooked to Recruited</p>
        </div>
        <div class=" w-[90%] flex items-center justify-center gap-16 pb-16 max-lg:flex-col max-lg:w-full">
            <div class="w-[55%] flex justify-start items-center relative max-lg:w-full">
                <div class="relative  ">
                    <Image src={player} format="svg" alt="logo"   class="w-[80%]  h-[616px] max-lg:w-full max-lg:h-full rounded-2xl" />
                </div>
                <div class=" flex justify-between items-center flex-col w-[490px] h-[231px] max-lg:w-[95%]  tracking-[0%] text-white z-10 bg-black absolute bottom-0 left-[120px] max-lg:bottom-[-120px] max-lg:left-[2.5%] rounded-2xl border-1 border-[#9EA1A1] p-6    bg-[linear-gradient(0deg,#010101,#010101),radial-gradient(68.37%_68.37%_at_50%_31.63%,rgba(173,173,173,0.2)_0%,rgba(1,1,1,0.2)_100%)]  shadow-[0px_0px_120px_20px_rgba(203,203,203,0.15)]">
                    <div class="text-[22px]  relative after:content-[url('/assets/quotation.svg')] after:absolute after:left-[-30px] after:top-[-70px]   max-lg:after:left-[-38px]">
                        <p class="font-[400]"><span class="font-[600]"> </span>I had the talent— getting the right oppurtunity changed everything.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full text-right text-[22px]">
                        <p class="font-semibold">Thomas Miles</p>
                        <p>From Overlooked to Pro</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-[45%] flex justify-end items-center flex-col max-lg:w-full">
                <div class="font-normal text-[20px] leading-[27px] w-[90%] max-lg:w-[95%] max-lg:text-[16px] max-lg:mt-[112px] tracking-normal text-white relative">
                    <p>Thomas Miles battled through multiple transfers, COVID disruptions, and limited  playing time, yet his dedication never wavered. When he needed a fresh start, HoopsToCollege helped him land at Warner Pacific—his perfect fit—where he earned All-Conference honors and secured a fully covered education.</p>
                    <p class="mt-5">Now, Thomas is living his dream, starting his professional career in Germany. His journey proves that with resilience and the right support, overlooked athletes can achieve their goals. Stories like his drive HoopsToCollege’s mission to help players find the best path to success.</p>
                </div>             
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
